# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  BrandBook Client OS — Production Environment Template (Supabase)
#
#  SETUP:
#    cp .env.production.example .env
#    # Edit .env with your real values, then:
#    docker compose up -d --build
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Supabase Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get this from: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → Database → URI
# IMPORTANT: URL-encode special chars in the password:
#   @ → %40   $ → %24   # → %23   % → %25
# Example: password "Pass@123$" becomes "Pass%40123%24"
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:YOUR_PASSWORD_URL_ENCODED@db.zkdbrajxjvxvrfrypknw.supabase.co:5432/postgres

# ── JWT Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate: openssl rand -base64 64
JWT_SECRET=change_me_very_long_random_string_at_least_64_chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# ── Your public domain ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# With Nginx same-domain routing CORS is handled automatically.
# Comma-separate multiple domains if needed.
FRONTEND_URL=https://yourdomain.com

# ── MinIO file storage ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STORAGE_ACCESS_KEY=brandbook
STORAGE_SECRET_KEY=change_me_strong_minio_password
STORAGE_BUCKET=brandbook-files
STORAGE_REGION=us-east-1

# ── Optional: WhatsApp Cloud API ──────────────────────────────────────────────
WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://graph.facebook.com/v18.0
WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=
WHATSAPP_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# ── Optional: Email (SMTP / SendGrid) ─────────────────────────────────────────
SMTP_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=apikey
SMTP_PASS=
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@yourdomain.com

# ── Optional: Meta Webhook ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
META_VERIFY_TOKEN=change_me_random_token
META_APP_SECRET=

# ── Optional: Google Ads ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_ADS_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_ADS_CLIENT_SECRET=
GOOGLE_ADS_DEVELOPER_TOKEN=
